nextCommand


java.lang.String nextCommand()

                       throws java.io.IOException
The next command or move from THIS. Uses the format of commands documented in the specification. A return value of null indicates that THIS has nothing to do at this point (for example, when its game is in set-up mode, an automated player never issues commands).
